{"tid":2281233,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"睇到泛民俾中共DQ，我個心好唔舒服但係喊唔出。","createTime":"2020-11-11T05:29:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-11T11:38:48.000Z","uid":363990,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"232139d2fc891b73bb3cb3aa4ccaf5fb548815bb","tid":2281233,"uid":363990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T05:29:21.000Z","msg":"我有抑鬱、焦慮、PTSD。<br />\n見到泛民想總辭，但係做唔到，其實我好想笑佢哋<br />\n但係諗到街頭抗爭冇曬、國際線用國安法封鎖、依家議會戰線都無埋。<br />\n其實我真係好灰好想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我成日都同自己講，話香港總有一日會得救。<br />\n但係經過今日之後，突然間覺得我地嘅生存空間好渺茫。<br />\n突然好想放棄我自己嘅夢想，去讀專科移民算。<br />\n我真係再抵受唔到嚟場運動嘅資訊，我一見到會諗起好多以前戰火連天嘅畫面，我真係好驚好驚。<br />\n我之前覺得自己會好堅強，19歲仔已經可以頂住呢啲壓力。<br />\n不過近排開始不停發惡夢，個人試過係街聽到有人追賊我嚇到坐低。<br />\n我真係好迷茫，好想放棄...<br />\n<br />\n我會同大家一齊努力捱過嚟個時刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望果16隻字會係香港人嚟個民族嘅心入面扎根，茁壯成長。"},{"pid":"de9a3896544d32419ec0463686ddab7ba88ec921","tid":2281233,"uid":2419,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T05:31:02.000Z","msg":"議會戰線其實冇左好耐啦<br />\n<br />\n咁諗會唔會舒服d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba2c926e2d0518fe8a4804e54ed006e44c848776","tid":2281233,"uid":363990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de9a3896544d32419ec0463686ddab7ba88ec921","tid":2281233,"uid":2419,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T05:31:02.000Z","msg":"議會戰線其實冇左好耐啦<br />\n<br />\n咁諗會唔會舒服d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T05:32:31.000Z","msg":"可能會嘅<br />\n連香港嘅核心價值：三權分立都可以埋沒<br />\n中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a6904d48722dfe2f3cd3f2db8ff1669e4bd418a","tid":2281233,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T05:34:09.000Z","msg":"有時都會覺得充滿冇力感<br />\n如果太大壓力時 抖抖 短暫抽離下先"},{"pid":"21e0cb0d870a138ff1d730b9c7820435719d2854","tid":2281233,"uid":363990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a6904d48722dfe2f3cd3f2db8ff1669e4bd418a","tid":2281233,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T05:34:09.000Z","msg":"有時都會覺得充滿冇力感<br />\n如果太大壓力時 抖抖 短暫抽離下先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T05:35:27.000Z","msg":"其實要抽離真係好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e969120184e1b4c334a32f3a8a39fd748a033f38","tid":2281233,"uid":304321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T06:40:49.000Z","msg":"認真 如果真係太辛苦 巴打不坊唔好接受咁多資訊住<br />\n做一排港豬等自己情況好D先 你抑鬱焦慮再加埋PTSD三樣野溝埋一齊<br />\n你要照顧好自己先啊"},{"pid":"947e486b87bf38eb6c0b234e575781c00352e449","tid":2281233,"uid":374184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T11:38:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1f5a6dd47a05e1c7080acb709424a7af9b85e634","tid":2281233,"uid":374184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T11:38:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}